   <conbody>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Check that the gateway is firmly mounted.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Check that the cable from the network management card (NMC)
is connected to a Modbus-TCP port at the bottom of the gateway.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Connect the regulated 24 V (20.4 V to 28.8 V) DC power source
cable.<note class="- topic/note ">Use a 60/75 or 75°C (140/167 or 167°F) copper
(CU) wire.</note>
            </p>
            <table class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="COLSPEC2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry morerows="2" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <image href="../Images/IP_AB9006_Power-supply_0000588164.svg"
                                  placement="inline"
                                  class="- topic/image "/>
                        </entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A) </b>+24 V DC</entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B) </b>GND</entry>
                     </row>
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(C) </b>Protective earth (ground)</entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Tighten the terminals with a torque of 0.5–0.8 Nm (5–7
lbs-in).</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Turn on the power supply.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Continue with <xref href="AB900x_Set_IP_With_Local_Connection_CPT_0000588216.dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="concept"
                     class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
